1. Ja sam bio u Africi prošle godine. (*Africi*) (I was in Africa last year.)
2. Koja je najveća životinja u Africi? (*Africi*) (What is the largest animal in Africa?)
3. Kao dete, želela sam da idem u Afriku i vidim lavove. (*Afriku*) (As a child, I wanted to go to Africa and see lions.)
4. Oni su otišli u Afriku na safari. (*Afriku*) (They went to Africa on a safari.)
5. Stanovnici Afrike imaju različite kulture i običaje. (*Afrike*) (The inhabitants of Africa have different cultures and traditions.)
6. U Africi je divno vreme tokom cele godine. (*Africi*) (The weather in Africa is great all year round.)
7. Afrika je dom za različite vrste životinja koje ne žive nigde drugde. (*Afrika*) (Africa is home to various species of animals that don't live anywhere else.)
8. Ova knjiga opisuje putovanje kroz Afriku od Maroka do Južne Afrike. (*Afriku*) (This book describes a journey through Africa from Morocco to South Africa.)
9. Veliki deo Afrike se nalazi u tropskoj zoni. (*Afrike*) (A large part of Africa is located in the tropical zone.)
10. Moja prijateljica se preselila u Afriku i tamo sada radi kao volonter. (*Afriku*) (My friend moved to Africa and now works there as a volunteer.)